---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="Diseños de Branding | Digital Solutions">
  
  <!-- HERO DESIGN (Corporate Blue) -->
  <section class="relative bg-[#1d4ed8] text-white pt-32 pb-16 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden flex items-center">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-2/3 h-full bg-[#2563eb] rounded-bl-full opacity-50 pointer-events-none transform translate-x-1/4"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 w-full flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-16 fade-in-up">
      
      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 text-center md:text-left">
        <div class="inline-block bg-[#3b82f6] text-white px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest shadow-sm mb-6">
          Branding & Identity
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-black tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] lg:leading-[0.85] text-white mb-8">
          Diseños de<br />
          <span class="text-[#93c5fd]">Branding<span class="text-white">.</span></span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-blue-100 leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-lg font-medium mx-auto md:mx-0">
          No creamos simples interfaces; construimos sistemas visuales completos que refuerzan la confianza corporativa e impulsan la tasa de conversión.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start">
          <a href="https://wa.me/584124683230" class="bg-white text-[#1d4ed8] px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:bg-blue-50 transition-all shadow-xl">Reservar Proyecto</a>
          <a href={`${base}portafolio`} class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:bg-white/20 transition-all">Ver Portafolio</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Abstract Visual Box (matching landing-page style) -->
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative hidden lg:block">
        <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4f46e5] to-[#2563eb] rounded-[3.5rem] rotate-3 relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-white/10 group flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-600/10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center opacity-20 group-hover:rotate-12 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-700">
            <svg class="w-48 h-48 text-white relative z-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:40px_40px]"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FEATURES / LENGUAJE VISUAL -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-[#f8fafc]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      
      <div class="mb-20 text-center md:text-left">
          <span class="text-[#2563eb] font-black text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase block mb-4">Fundamentos</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-[#0f172a] tracking-tighter leading-none mb-6">
            Lenguaje <span class="text-[#2563eb]">Corporativo.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            Aplicamos principios sólidos y probados para construir una percepción premium que guía instintivamente al Lead hacia la compra.
          </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <!-- Block 1 -->
        <div class="eng-hover p-10 border border-slate-100 bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-xl transition-all h-full">
          <div class="mb-10 text-slate-400 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-[#2563eb]">Paso 01</span>
            <span class="bg-blue-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px]">Minimalismo</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#eff6ff] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#2563eb]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 12l8.954-8.955c.44-.439 1.152-.439 1.591 0L21.75 12M4.5 9.75v10.125c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125H9.75v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21h4.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.75M8.25 21h8.25"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-[#0f172a] mb-4 tracking-tight">Diseño Premium</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">Eliminamos el desorden visual. Nos enfocamos en el diseño asimétrico para transmitir rigor empresarial absoluto.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Block 2 (Typography) -->
        <div class="eng-hover col-span-1 md:col-span-2 bg-[#1e40af] rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 md:p-14 flex flex-col justify-between text-white hover:shadow-2xl transition-all overflow-hidden relative group">
          <div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 text-[20rem] font-black opacity-[0.05] leading-none pointer-events-none select-none group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-1000">Aa</div>
          <div class="mb-10 text-[#93c5fd] font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest relative z-10 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-8 h-px bg-[#93c5fd]/50"></span> 02 / TIPOGRAFÍA
          </div>
          <div class="relative z-10 w-full md:w-3/4">
            <h3 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-none">Estructura Escrita.</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 text-xl leading-relaxed font-medium">
              La tipografía es el contrato silencioso de tu marca. Optimizamos legibilidad corporativa, tamaños y pesos para garantizar máxima profesionalidad en cada párrafo.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-white/10 flex justify-between text-[#93c5fd] text-2xl font-black tracking-[0.5em] relative z-10">
            <span>Aa</span> <span>Bb</span> <span>Cc</span> <span>Dd</span> <span>Ee</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Block 3 -->
        <div class="eng-hover col-span-1 md:col-span-2 p-10 md:p-14 border border-slate-100 bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <div class="mb-10 text-[#2563eb] font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] relative flex items-center gap-2">
             <span class="w-8 h-px bg-[#2563eb]/30"></span> 03 / SISTEMAS
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
               <h3 class="text-4xl font-black text-[#0f172a] mb-6 tracking-tighter">Arquitectura Modular.</h3>
               <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm font-medium">
                 Construimos catálogos de componentes reusables, facilitando la escalabilidad del sistema manteniento un orden y diseño impoluto al paso de los años.
               </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Mock UI Panel -->
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-5 bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 shadow-inner">
               <div class="flex items-center gap-4 w-full h-14 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-5 shadow-sm"> 
                 <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-[#1e40af]"></div> 
                 <div class="h-3 w-1/3 bg-slate-100 rounded-full"></div>
               </div>
               <div class="w-full h-14 bg-[#2563eb] rounded-xl shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(37,99,235,0.3)] flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]">
                 Call To Action
               </div>
               <div class="w-full h-14 bg-white border-2 border-[#2563eb] text-[#2563eb] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-blue-50 transition-all">
                 Alt Button
               </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Block 4 -->
        <div class="eng-hover p-10 bg-[#2563eb] rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-2xl transition-all text-white group overflow-hidden relative">
          <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 opacity-10 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-700">
             <svg class="w-40 h-40" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-10 text-white/50 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest relative z-10">
            04 / UX ACTION
          </div>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h3 class="text-4xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tighter leading-none">Micro <br/>Interacciones.</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed">
              Animaciones que dan un feedback profesional e impecable ante las interacciones del Lead para guiarlo a la conversión.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- UX STRATEGY & AUDIT -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-white border-t border-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-20">
        <!-- Text -->
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
          <span class="text-[#2563eb] font-black text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase block mb-6">User Centered Design</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-[#0f172a] tracking-tighter leading-none mb-10">
            Arquitectura de <span class="text-[#2563eb]">Conversión.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12 font-medium">
            El diseño web corporativo no consiste simplemente en hacer que las cosas se vean atractivas; consiste en guiar a los usuarios de manera psicológica hacia una acción concreta.
          </p>
          
          <ul class="space-y-8">
            <li class="eng-hover flex items-start gap-6 p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-slate-50/50 border border-transparent hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-sm">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white text-[#2563eb] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z"></path></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-[#0f172a] text-xl block mb-2 font-black tracking-tight">Wireframing de Precisión</strong>
                <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">Bocetamos la jerarquía completa antes de aplicar la gráfica, garantizando solidez estructural.</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="eng-hover flex items-start gap-6 p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-slate-50/50 border border-transparent hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-sm">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white text-[#2563eb] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-[#0f172a] text-xl block mb-2 font-black tracking-tight">Reducción de Fricción</strong>
                <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">Simplificamos CTAs para acelerar drásticamente la toma de decisiones financieras de tus clientes.</span>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Visual Flow -->
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
           <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-slate-100 p-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-slate-200 shadow-inner relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col gap-6">
              <div class="w-full h-16 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm flex items-center px-6 gap-4 border border-slate-100">
                 <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-200"></div>
                 <div class="h-3 w-1/3 bg-slate-100 rounded-full"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-6">
                 <div class="w-2/3 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 border border-slate-100">
                    <div class="h-3 w-1/2 bg-slate-100 rounded-full mb-6"></div>
                    <div class="space-y-3">
                       <div class="h-2 w-full bg-slate-50 rounded-full"></div>
                       <div class="h-2 w-4/5 bg-slate-50 rounded-full"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-12 h-12 w-full bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-dashed border-slate-200"></div>
                 </div>
                 <div class="w-1/3 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border-2 border-[#2563eb] p-6 relative">
                    <div class="absolute -right-3 -top-3 w-8 h-8 bg-[#2563eb] text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg></div>
                    <div class="h-3 w-1/2 bg-blue-50 rounded-full mb-10"></div>
                    <div class="h-14 w-full bg-[#2563eb] rounded-xl"></div>
                 </div>
              </div>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BRANDING INTEGRAL (Dark Blue Section) -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-[#0f172a] relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Glow -->
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full max-w-4xl h-full bg-[#1d4ed8] opacity-10 blur-[150px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center mb-24">
        <span class="text-[#3b82f6] font-black text-sm tracking-[0.4em] uppercase block mb-4">ENGINEERING BRANDING</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-white leading-none mb-8 tracking-tighter">
          Identidad <span class="text-[#3b82f6]">Implacable.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 font-medium text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Más que un logo; forjamos el ADN visual de tu empresa para imponer autoridad frente a la competencia.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Logo Design -->
        <div class="eng-hover glow-on-hover bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 rounded-[2.5rem] p-12 hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition-all group backdrop-blur-md">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-900/30 text-[#60a5fa] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-white/5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-none">Arquitectura Maestro.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">Conceptualización basada en proporciones áureas para logotipos responsivos y vectoriales de máxima nitidez.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Brandbook -->
        <div class="eng-hover glow-on-hover bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 rounded-[2.5rem] p-12 hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition-all group backdrop-blur-md relative transform lg:-translate-y-6">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-[#2563eb] text-white text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] px-5 py-2 rounded-full">Standard Gold</div>
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-900/30 text-[#60a5fa] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-white/5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-none">Manual Sagrado.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">Leyes de identidad: retículas, contrastes, tono de voz y estilo fotográfico bajo un rigor técnico absoluto.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Paletas -->
        <div class="eng-hover glow-on-hover bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 rounded-[2.5rem] p-12 hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition-all group backdrop-blur-md">
           <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-900/30 text-[#60a5fa] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-white/5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-none">Psicología Cromática.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">Selección metódica formulada para engatillar respuestas emocionales que impulsen la confianza y la compra.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRECIO SECTION -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#2563eb] font-black text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase block mb-4">Full Brand Package</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-[#0f172a] tracking-tighter leading-none mb-10">Idenitdad <span class="text-[#2563eb]">Maestra.</span></h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="eng-hover glow-on-hover relative bg-white rounded-[3.5rem] p-12 lg:p-16 border border-slate-100 shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(37,99,235,0.08)] overflow-hidden group hover:border-[#2563eb] transition-all duration-700">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-12 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-[0.08] transition-opacity">
          <svg class="w-48 h-48 text-[#2563eb]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-12">
            <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm font-black line-through mb-1 uppercase tracking-widest">$280 USD</span>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 sm:gap-4">
              <span class="text-7xl sm:text-9xl font-black text-[#2563eb] tracking-tighter">$180</span>
              <span class="text-slate-400 text-base sm:text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Total</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-y-6 gap-x-12 text-left mb-16 w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto border-y border-slate-100 py-12">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-bold text-sm"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#2563eb]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Manual de Marca Avanzado</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-bold text-sm"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#2563eb]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Logotipo Vectorial Maestro</li>
